        "accept_rate" : 72,
        "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/KzMc4.jpg?s=256",
        "display_name" : "E-Riz",
        "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/639520/e-riz"
      },
      "edited" : false,
      "score" : 0,
      "creation_date" : 1677610372,
      "post_id" : 75593693,
      "comment_id" : 133371003,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "PUT should not generally be used for creating resources, that should be a POST. PUT should address a specific resource for <i>updating</i> (usually by ID). Thus, a 201 response is not appropriate for a PUT."
    } ],
