    "question_id" : 75593543,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>For PUT</p>\n<ul>\n<li>HTTP status 201 if the entry does not exist and is created</li>\n<li>HTTP status 200 or HTTP status 204 if entry exists and is updated</li>\n</ul>\n<p>For DELETE</p>\n<ul>\n<li>HTTP status 200</li>\n</ul>\n<p>visit   <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Methods/PUT\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Mozilla docs</a> for further details</p>\n"
  }, {
